4. Oni su snosili *krivicu* za propust. (They bore the fault for the mistake.)
5. On je preuzeo *krivicu*. (He assumed the fault.)
6. Ona je priznala svoju *krivicu*. (She admitted her fault.)
7. Nastala je *krivica*. (The fault arose.)
8. On nije trebalo da preuzme *krivicu*. (He shouldn't have taken the fault.)